snippet.title: Chaos Reborn trailer
snippet.description:
Chaos Reborn is the new strategy and tactical RPG from the designer of the original X-COM. It is being released on Steam Early Access on December 9th 2014 for PC, Mac, and Linux.

Concept art by Svetoslav Petrov. Music by George Strezov.
